====================================================
- xvid cvs-20100901
1) # cvs -d:pserver:anonymous@cvs.xvid.org:/xvid login
    (just type enter)
2) # cvs -d:pserver:anonymous@cvs.xvid.org:/xvid co xvidcore
3) cd xvidcore/build/generic
4) ./bootstrap.sh
5) ./configure --prefix=/usr
6) make
7) library libxvidcore.so.4.2 is located under =build/



